---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout
  title="About Us – Severino Realty"
  description="Learn more about Severino Realty, our mission, and the values that guide us as a trusted real estate agency in Nairobi.">

  <section class="py-12 max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-4">About Severino Realty</h1>
    <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-6">
      Severino Realty is a Nairobi‑based real estate agency committed to connecting buyers, sellers,
      and renters with exceptional properties. Our experienced team combines local market knowledge
      with a passion for service to deliver a seamless real estate experience.
    </p>

    <h2 id="mission" class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary mb-3">Our Mission</h2>
    <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-6">
      Our mission is to empower our clients with the information and support they need to make confident
      real estate decisions. We strive to provide honest advice, transparent processes, and personalised
      service in every interaction.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary mb-3">Our Values</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-neutral-700 space-y-2">
      <li>
        <strong>Integrity:</strong> We conduct our business with the highest ethical standards.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Expertise:</strong> We stay up‑to‑date on market trends and regulations to guide our clients.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Respect:</strong> We listen carefully and treat everyone with courtesy.
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>

</MainLayout>
